 3.) Find all my encodes you have and COPY them in that newly created directory - when asked OVERWRITE empty files

 6.) Press Start

 Please, do not just leech. You are better than the rest. Exchange bytes given during the download - that would be only way to finish at all - dark_defender and myself (for a help, just for short time) would seed with activated Initial seeding.
